♪ MIGHTY ♪
- ♪ LA, LA, HEY ♪

00:14.764 --> 00:16.516
- ♪ MIGHTY ♪
- ♪ LA, LA, WOW ♪

00:16.599 --> 00:18.226
- ♪ COME ON, EVERYBODY,
